@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_dtobtc(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.sin((v2 + 0.79 + v1 + 0.30)))
    tmp = wp.abs((0.79 - (tmp + 0.81 + v1 + 0.66)))
    v0 = ((tmp * wp.exp(v1 + 0.29)) / v2)
    v2 = v1
    tmp = ((wp.sin(tmp + 1.00) + v2) + wp.exp((tmp + 0.75 / tmp + 0.68)))
    tmp = (wp.sin((v0 + 0.77 + v0 + 0.79)) - wp.sin((v1 + 0.20 - tmp + 0.75)))
    v1 = v2
    data[tid] = v0
